Things I Do
Strategy
Theres no style over substance here. I bring together form and the function to create something that looks good and performs brilliantly. Simple.
Information Architecture
Its about organizing the content and flow of a website based on research and planning. Eventually I come up with a structure/design that balances the users desires with the businesss needs.
Design & Development
As a designer and developer, I understand the perfect
user interface should look good and work even better.
Alongside my clients, I uncover problems and solve them.
In short, I create bolder online experiences.
